      • RENAME_FILE_VIA_CONTEXT_MENU_TC

        public void RENAME_FILE_VIA_CONTEXT_MENU_TC()
        Summary
        Rename file via context menu
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        Steps
        1. Right click on document
        2. Click on 'Rename' option.
        3. Enter desired name
        4. Click on OK button
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify that document is renamed.
